text: Dominique Souchet (born July 9, 1946 in La Rochelle, Charente-Maritime) was a member of the National Assembly of France between 2008 and 2012. He represented the Vendée department,http://www.assemblee- nationale.fr/13/tribun/fiches_id/412525.asp is a member of the Movement for France and does not align himself with any parliamentary group. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:Living people Category:People from La Rochelle Category:Politicians from Nouvelle-Aquitaine Category:Movement for France politicians Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Movement for France MEPs Category:MEPs for France 1999–2004
